reviewText: This movie was truly poorly made and lacks director know how.  This ended up in my file thirteen and certainly won't be missed.

This video is nowhere near as good as the original Perfect Pair. The description says "twice as many"; I'd say there are half as many. The girls aren't as hot, and it takes at least 5 minutes of talking before they finally take it all off. Of all of the GGW videos that focus on the chest, this has got to be the most disappointing. Can't believe I pre-ordered this. Not getting my hopes up with these titles anymore; I won't pay full price for them anymore, anyway.
The movie was not very good and the girls that are on the cover aren't in the movie. Would not buy.
